DROP external table ExternalAggHighPollutionEvents
drop table high_pollution_events
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE ExternalAggHighPollutionEvents (
	date VARCHAR(100),
    high_pollution_events INT
)
WITH (
    LOCATION = 'gold/agg_high_pollution_events/part-00000-5145ceed-5e9d-41ef-9440-4187425396c5-c000.snappy.parquet',
    DATA_SOURCE = MyDataSource,
    FILE_FORMAT = ParquetFileFormat
);

CREATE TABLE HighPollutionEvents (
	date VARCHAR(100),
    high_pollution_events INT
);
INSERT INTO HighPollutionEvents (
    date,
    high_pollution_events
)
SELECT DISTINCT
    date,
    high_pollution_events
FROM ExternalAggHighPollutionEvents;
GO
